item.title: Help On My Server!
item.dc:creator: @X_F_U_R_Y_X X F U R Y X
item.description:
@X_F_U_R_Y_X wrote:

goto client.java, then press ctrl+h, then on the first box tpye the name of the current owner (the old one), then on the 2nd box, type the owner’s name you wish it to become (Like yours… :/), then press replace all, and save, compile and run server, then it should change it…
